@node About " About Dtr!LastCallers v1.o "

                  ·     __ ___________
                 /_    \\\\/           //
        .________ /_____\\            /
    ____|_      ///    /_\\___   _____ _____ ________.
   _\\     _     /           /   \\     \\     \\       |_
   /______\\_____\\    /     /     \\     \\     \\      _/
      -Mo!/aL-/____________\\\\    /___________/______|
                  «- --------\\  ř--------------------------------------- -»
                              \\/

This is a FIM based LastCallers for Fame. As it is a real door it offers many
features which cannot be provided by plain CLI tools.

So it can display the status of current connections and highlite one's
previous connections. But, best you see for yourself...

 «- ---------------------------------------------------------------------- -»

@endnode
