@node FAME? " About the F.inal A.miga M.ailbox E.ngine"                                      ·

           _ __ _ ______ _________________________________________ _
               _\\\\\\__   \\_ ______ _     _ ___________  _ _______
             _/    |/    _/   __///_____\\\\\\__   __   \\_\\\\\\_____/
             |     /______    \\|           |/   |/         _/____
             |     __/   |_    \\     _     /    /     _    \\     |
             |_    | sYz!  \\_________|\\___/____/      |\\____    _|
           _ __\\___| ________________________ /_______| __ |___/__ _

           [- bULLETIN bOARD sYSTEMS - ©'1994-1998 IN-Ovation Soft -]

 Because of the fact that many people asked for FAME, FAME has been released in
 february 1996 under the concept of shareware and is available for everyone.

 FAME is Shareware !

 This means that you are allowed to download the latest FAME Demoversion
 and to use it 30 days long. After 30 days and if you want to have an unlimited
 version of FAME you have to register.

 Currently the latest FAME Demoversion v1.23 has no real limitations.
 This Demoversion of FAME pops up a Shareware-Requester every time you open
 a Node-Screen also if someone is logging on a message will be displayed with
 a short delay which informs about the unregistered Demoversion.

 If you register FAME you will get the full version and from time to time
 updates with enhancements and bugfixes.

 FAME 2.0 is in progress and will be released soon.

 You will also get full support via e-mail and FAME distribution sites.

 We now also have a 24h online telnet board where you can get updates of FAME
 for registered users.

 There is also a mailinglist available for fast help.

 The future of the Software depends on YOU so please think about registering
 FAME !!!

 FAME price has been droped from DM 150,- (german marks) to DM 99,- (german marks)

 So FAME costs now DM 99,-

 There are following packages available:

 FAME BBS Standard
 Full version of FAME
 Price: DM 99,-

 FAME BBS + tools/doors from SieGeL/tRSi
 Full version of FAME and full versions of all tools and doors from SieGeL/tRSi.
 Price: DM 120,-

 If you are not german please get the current exchange rate from your currency
 to german marks and send it to me via the following possible ways.

 Please take care of the different prices for the enhanced packages.

 Send the price of the package you have choosen to the postal address below:

 David Wettig
 Feurigstr 37
 10827 Berlin

 Germany

 Or use my bank account:

             BLZ: 100 500 00
  Account-Number: 1160148798
	          Bank: Berliner Sparkasse
   Account-Owner: David Wettig

 Some banks are needing more datas (normally outside germany)

     Bank branch: 116
          Street: Hauptstr. 98/99
     Postal code: 10827 Berlin, Germany
      Bank Phone: +49 30 787972-0


 If you have questions or problems with FAME, please turn on one of the
 FAME-Developers or ask Strider to solve your problems.


 What is included in the FAME-package ?
 --------------------------------------
         Server - SystemEditor
       MainPart - FAMEHydra.FIM
FAMEFileChecker - FAMESModem.FIM
Various other tools and doors.

  FAMEError.FIM - FAME.library
                  FAMEChat.FIM      Programmed by Bloodrock/tRSi

 FAMEFullEd.FIM - FAMEScript.FIM    Programmed by Beatnik/tRSi

 MUI UserEditor - FAMEDoorHelp.FIM
                  FAMEInfo          Programmed by SieGeL/tRSi

 Also some doors and tools from the FAME-Development-Team are included,
 but these doors are only unregistered versions and have therefor some
 limitations. The registered versions of those doors and the informations
 how to get them are available in the pUNISHMENT iNC. BBS.


